Your Family Business, Your Family Net Worth

You have spent a lifetime building and safeguarding your business. Now it's
time to retire. If you are like most business owners, you have more
questions than answers. "What is my business really worth?" "Can I afford to
retire?" "How can I safeguard my net worth and protect my family?" "How can
I reduce taxes on the sale?" "Should I keep the business in the family, or
sell it to someone else?" And the biggest question of all: "How do I get
started?" Gary Pittsford, owner of Castle3, has answered these tough questions for business
owners time and time again...
